findings.title: startTime can be updated without taking in account stopTime
findings.description: The contract allows updating startTime without considering stopTime, which may lead to unintended behavior.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges, including changing start and stop times, withdrawing ERC20 tokens, pausing/unpausing the contract, and modifying stakingCap value.
